80000-FameContents-.name: The Alliance needs you! Press the ( ! ) balloon over your character's portrait.

80020-FameContents-.name: All systems green! Sorties are now available from the hologlobe!

80022-FameContents-.name: Overlook to Sapling One, mission is a go!

80023-FameContents-.name: Sapling One? Hahaha! Is that a Green Hoods call sign?

80024-FameContents-.name: Laugh all you want, I'm sure it's cuter than whatever Dark Wind uses!

80025-FameContents-.name: ...Cuteness doesn't factor into Dark Wind tactics.

80030-FameContents-.name: Mission complete! Come on home to Sky Fortress!

80040-FameContents-.name: Open the Reputation window to see your standing with each faction.

80050-FameContents-.name: You can find Field Missions on the World Map anytime.

80060-FameContents-.name: Good work! Return to the ship!

80080-FameContents-.name: Click where the arrow is pointing!

80081-FameContents-.name: Hey cadet! Over here, I've got something to tell you!

80090-FameContents-.name: $MyPCName$, I've received your evaluation reports. Let's have a brief chat.

93000123-FameContents-.name: Open your inventory and activate the support flare you've received to call for assistance.

93000158-FameContents-.name: <font color="#ffd200">$npcName:23000094$</font> is approaching Sky Fortress at high speeds! He's trying to board the ship!

91000020-FameContents-.name: The crew of this ship is so spoiled with their air transports! Back in my day, you made a grueling trek on horseback, just like everybody else!

91000022-FameContents-.name: While you're in the neighborhood, why don't you check up on Frey? I worry about leaving the empress's safety in the hands of someone so young.

91000023-FameContents-.name: Remember, all you need to do is power up the generators and insert that data disk into the comms array. We'll take care of the rest from here.

91000024-FameContents-.name: If we don't do anything, those Prizboxes will jam our transmission. I think it's time they were decommissioned, don't you agree?

91000026-FameContents-.name: While you're down there, why don't you do something about those berserk robots, so they don't damage the comms array?

91000027-FameContents-.name: Did you get the ledger? Head back to the ship so we can take a look!

91000033-FameContents-.name: Any luck with the ledger? Report back to Sky Fortress when you can.

91000034-FameContents-.name: Before we begin our investigation, we must secure the area. I trust you know what to do?

91000035-FameContents_EP1_02-.name: I'm detecting a $npcName:11003781$ in your vicinity! Be careful!

91000036-FameContents_EP1_02-.name: The goal of this exercise is to acclimate your body to extreme temperature conditions, but don't overdo it! If you're feeling faint, return to the ship.

91000037-FameContents_EP1_02-.name: Are you giving up? You're pathetic! If you can't kill it, keep on hitting it 'til it wishes it were dead! What do you mean I'm too harsh? Let go—*bzzt*

91000038-FameContents_EP1_02-.name: $MyPCName$, I've been monitoring remotely. There may be a solution to our quandary. Return to the carrier with $npcName:11000144$, and join me and the officers in the briefing room.
